Enum ScannerResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ScannerResults>
      • com.symbol.emdk.barcode.ScannerResults
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ScannerResults>

    public enum ScannerResults
extends java.lang.Enum<ScannerResults>
    Defines all the error codes the barcode scanning API returns.
